info.description:
Simple warehouse management system for Django 1.7+
==================================================

``django-warehouse`` is a simple warehouse management system for Django 1.7+

.. image:: https://travis-ci.org/dlancer/django-warehouse.svg?branch=master
    :target: https://travis-ci.org/dlancer/django-warehouse/
    :alt: Build status

.. image:: https://pypip.in/version/django-warehouse/badge.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-warehouse/
    :alt: Latest PyPI version

.. image:: https://pypip.in/download/django-warehouse/badge.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-warehouse/
    :alt: Number of PyPI downloads

.. image:: https://pypip.in/format/django-warehouse/badge.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-warehouse/
    :alt: Download format

.. image:: https://pypip.in/license/django-warehouse/badge.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/django-warehouse/
    :alt: License

Requirements
------------

::

    Django>=1.7.1
    django-appcore==0.0.3
    django-image-cropping==0.9
    easy-thumbnails==2.2
    PyYAML==3.11


Usage
=====

You may find detailed documentation is in the "docs" directory.
